Author: Bryan Jimenez

sender twister and receiver simulate the go back n protocol
sender and twister are implemented using threads instead of select


To compile:

	unzip
	make  

To run:

	./sender <listenPort> <destIP> <destPort> <interval> <win size>
	./twister <listenPort> <receiverIP> <receiverPort> <PC> <PD> <PO> <interval>
	./receiver <listenPort>

NOTE:
	intervals are in seconds	
	
